  "body": "## Issue\r\nEncountered in `v0.6.0`.\r\n\r\nWith `epoch = 0 (GENESIS_EPOCH)` [generate_seed](https://github.com/ethereum/eth2.0-specs/blob/v0.6.0/specs/core/0_beacon-chain.md#generate_seed) passes `epoch = GENESIS_EPOCH - 1` value to `get_randao_mix`:\r\n```python\r\n...\r\n    return hash(\r\n        get_randao_mix(state, epoch - MIN_SEED_LOOKAHEAD) +\r\n...\r\n```\r\nWith `epoch = -1` [get_randao_mix](https://github.com/ethereum/eth2.0-specs/blob/v0.6.0/specs/core/0_beacon-chain.md#get_randao_mix) throws an assertion error as condition \r\n`epoch <= get_current_epoch(state)` gets violated.",
